ontent type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;屏幕上精确查找功能中的 iPhone 移动消息&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jt5cyRtPzwGiZjX8T-W8YqtyXKw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73001537/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0380.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hwYN33&quot;>;Apple 有赢得了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/26/24012382/apple-import-ban-watch-series-9-ultra-2&quot;>;Apple Watch 禁令的暂时暂停&lt; /a>; 于周二生效，因此它将 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/27/24016684/apple-watch-on-sale-again-import-sales- bans-paused&quot;>;从今天开始&lt;/a>;（周三）在 Apple Store 零售店恢复销售，并于明天（12 月 28 日）下午 3 点/中午 12 点（东部时间）在 Apple.com 上恢复销售。联邦上诉法院今天下令暂停进口和销售禁令，此前苹果公司要求暂停进口和销售禁令，至少要等到美国海关确定其对 Apple Watch 所做的改变是否足以避免导致禁令的专利纠纷。 。海关预计将于 1 月 12 日发布决定。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eqjJvR&quot;>;法院的命令意味着苹果可以暂时恢复销售 Apple Watch Series 9 和 Apple Watch Ultra 2。两款手表均被&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/21/24010965/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-removed-from-online-sale-store&quot;>;拉下上周从其网站&lt;/a>;上架，本周下架，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/27/24016464/ apple-watch-itc-ban-paused&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/27/24016464/apple-watch-itc-ban-paused" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/27/24016464/apple-watch-itc-ban-paused</id><author><name>雅各布·卡斯特雷纳克斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-27T09:30:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-27T09:30:00-05:00</updated><title> 2023 年 10 款精彩 Windows PC 游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;矢量拼贴画，以游戏控制器形状呈现博德之门 3 的艺术作品。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FvYK365kwaSHvjAR0YcMYUWx6w4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73001081/236889_EOY_PC_CVirginia.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;The Verge / 图片由 L